OL,3,CWomen who tortured man over false
OL,4,Cpaedophile claim jailed for murder
OL,6,FTwo women who tortured a "kind and
OL,7,Fgentle" man to death after falsely
OL,8,Faccusing him of being a paedophile
OL,9,Fhave been jailed for his murder.
OL,11,FZoe Rider and Nicola Lethbridge at his
OL,12,Fhome in Fraser Drive, Woodseats,
OL,13,FSheffield, on 9 August last year.
OL,15,FSheffield Crown Court heard drug users
OL,16,FRider, 36, and Lethbridge, 45, had
OL,17,Fgone to his property to rob him to
OL,18,Ffund their habits.
