OL,6,FDuring the course of the robbery, the
OL,7,Fpair accused him of being a child sex
OL,8,Foffender and launched what Judge Sarah
OL,9,FWright called a "vicious and joint
OL,10,Fattack", part of which they filmed.
OL,12,FIn the footage, some of which was
OL,13,Fshown to the jury at their trial, Mr
OL,14,FKoszyczarski could be heard pleading
OL,15,Fwith them, saying: "I can't stop
OL,16,Fbleeding."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
