OL,6,FThe judge told the defendants: "You
OL,7,Fthreatened to mutilate him and shouted
OL,8,Fobscenities on him. You failed to
OL,9,Flisten to his denials or to offer him
OL,10,Fany compassion when he was clearly
OL,11,Finjured.
OL,13,F"The purpose of your attack was to
OL,14,Fsteal from him and to humiliate,
OL,15,Fterrify and hurt him."
OL,17,FMr Koszyczarski suffered 22 separate
OL,18,Finjuries to his face and body,
OL,19,Fincluding a broken nose, and a fatal
OL,20,Fbleed on the brain.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
