OL,6,FRider and Lethbridge denied murder,
OL,7,Fbut were found guilty following a
OL,8,Ftrial last month.
OL,10,FJudge Wright said there was "no
OL,11,Finformation" Mr Koszyczarski had any
OL,12,Fsexual interest in children.
OL,14,FIn a statement given in court, Mr
OL,15,FKoszyczarski's former partner Mary
OL,16,FJones said he was "kind and gentle".
