OL,6,FShe added: "It's heartbreaking I won't
OL,7,Fsee him again. I cry most days and
OL,8,Fnights. He was a special man. He would
OL,9,Fhelp anyone and had a heart of gold.
OL,10,FWhy have they murdered him when he
OL,11,Fshould still be alive, enjoying his
OL,12,Flife? Since he was taken from me I
OL,13,Flook at his photograph - he's smiling
OL,14,Fin that photo.
OL,16,F"I will love Stephen and miss him from
OL,17,Fthe rest of my life."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
