OL,6,FJailing the pair for life with a
OL,7,Fminimum term of 26 years, Judge Wright
OL,8,Fsaid: "No sentence I impose can ever
OL,9,Fcompensate Stephen's family and
OL,10,Ffriends for his loss. The manner of
OL,11,Fhis death and the very upsetting
OL,12,Frecording of part of the incident is
OL,13,Fvery traumatic for them and they will
OL,14,Fhave to live with that for the rest of
OL,15,Ftheir lives."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
