OL,6,FIn a statement after their
OL,7,Fconvictions, Det Ch Insp Tom Woodward,
OL,8,Fof South Yorkshire Police, said:
OL,9,F"Stephen was described as a quiet man.
OL,10,FAlthough he had a close circle of
OL,11,Ffriends, he kept himself to himself
OL,12,Fand just went about his business. He
OL,13,Fdidn't cause any problems or hurt
OL,14,Fanyone and his death was callous.
OL,16,F"Lethbridge and Rider had not only
OL,17,Fsubjected Stephen to mental torture
OL,18,Fand physical abuse but they humiliated
OL,19,Fhim during the attack wrongly accusing
OL,20,Fhim of being a paedophile which was
OL,21,Fsimply not the case."
